1:1: COMMENT NOTE
1:7: STR_LIT "
    斯篇專演「九九乘法」之理。
    考《管子》、《算數書》皆載九九之術，乃算家之樞紐。
    茲以雙重迴圈與明斷之法，羅列乘算口訣，以驗編譯器之全功。
"
7:1: COMMENT NOTE
7:6: STR_LIT " 甲為乘數，肇始於一，至九乃極 "
8:1: HERE_IS_A has a
8:7: VAR_TYPE num
8:11: NUMBER_LIT 1
8:13: NAME_IT name it
8:21: IDENT '甲'
9:1: WHILE_TRUE while true
9:13: IF if
9:16: IDENT '甲'
9:20: EXP_LOGIC >=
9:23: NUMBER_LIT 10
9:26: TOPIC topic
9:32: BREAK break
9:38: END end
10:5: COMMENT NOTE
10:10: STR_LIT " 乙為被乘數，亦自一始，隨甲流轉 "
11:5: HERE_IS_A has a
11:11: VAR_TYPE num
11:15: NUMBER_LIT 1
11:17: NAME_IT name it
11:25: IDENT '乙'
12:5: WHILE_TRUE while true
12:17: IF if
12:20: IDENT '乙'
12:24: EXP_LOGIC >=
12:27: NUMBER_LIT 10
12:30: TOPIC topic
12:36: BREAK break
12:42: END end
13:9: COMMENT NOTE
13:14: STR_LIT " 步其積：果 = 甲乘乙 "
14:9: EXP_MATH *
14:13: IDENT '甲'
14:17: ->
14:20: IDENT '乙'
14:24: NAME_IT name it
14:32: IDENT '果'
15:9: COMMENT NOTE
15:14: STR_LIT " 觀其積：若滿十，逕直書之；若不及十，加『得』字以齊句讀 "
16:9: IF if
16:12: IDENT '果'
16:16: EXP_LOGIC >=
16:19: NUMBER_LIT 10
16:22: TOPIC topic
16:28: HERE_ARE i have
16:35: NUMBER_LIT 3
16:37: VAR_TYPE str
16:42: SAID called
16:49: IDENT '甲'
16:53: SAID called
16:60: IDENT '乙'
16:64: SAID called
16:71: IDENT '果'
16:75: PRINT print
17:9: ELSE else
17:14: HERE_ARE i have
17:21: NUMBER_LIT 4
17:23: VAR_TYPE str
17:28: SAID called
17:35: IDENT '甲'
17:39: SAID called
17:46: IDENT '乙'
17:50: SAID called
17:57: STR_LIT "得"
17:63: SAID called
17:70: IDENT '果'
17:74: PRINT print
17:80: END end
